songs.title: Haulin (Best Teef in the Game Tour Trailer)
songs.lyrics:
Yeah
Pullout mash forward
Smelling like a a gas leak
Pullout the black bomber
Engine in the back seat Haulin
Why I feel like Tony Starks
We used to use the iron with the starch
My own lady is so spoiled
My old Chevy got new chrome on it
Pullout mash forward
I bet they never catch me
Feels like Tony Starks
Ouuu the irony
Cool out in that corner
I don't want to network
Pocket full of business cards
I think I'm too nice, i'm too charming
She told her me life was straight forward
She wanted a ticket but can't pay for it
We falling in love, we falling in love
Best teef in the game is all that she wants
